OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be a dry day and cloudy
OL,6,Fat times but still with some good
OL,7,Fbright and sunny spells, the best of
OL,8,Fthese will be early morning and again
OL,9,Ffrom late afternoon. Light
OL,10,Fnorthwesterly winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA dry night in the west with
OL,13,Flong clear spells. In the east it will
OL,14,Fbe cloudy with a few showers possible
OL,15,Fover Lothian and Borders. Light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
