OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FSunny spells in the west
OL,6,Fduring the morning, cloudier with a
OL,7,Ffew showers in the east. Cloud
OL,8,Fspreading west in the afternoon, with
OL,9,Fisolated showers moving west into
OL,10,FDumfries.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FHigh
OL,13,Fpressure dominates bringing a dry and
OL,14,Fsettled few days with light winds.
OL,15,FPlenty of bright and sunny spells,
OL,16,Fespecially in the west with the east
OL,17,Foften cloudier.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
